title: The U.S. economy is booming. So why are tech companies laying off workers?
description: Google, Amazon, Microsoft and a raft of others fired thousands of workers in January, continuing a layoff wave that began in 2022.

title: The wild probe into investors of DWAC, Trump Media’s proposed merger ally
description: An investigation into early investors of Digital World Acquisition included a government informant, a secret phone scan and an elite anti-money-laundering squad. It’s still going.
